	Julia children    
	 Los Angeles, July 18 (PTI): Hollywood actress Julia Roberts has said she will only be working in epic movies in order to spend more time with her children.      
	The 42-year-old star, who has three children with husband Daniel Moder, admits that this was the reason for her to star in her new film Eat, Pray, Love, Showbiz Spy has reported.    
	Mel house    
	 London (PTI): Actor Mel Gibson is reportedly planning to leave the US after selling off his mansion near New York. The Lethal Weapon star, who faces allegations of violence from his former Russian girlfriend Oksana Grigorieva, sold the mock Tudor property, known as Old Mill Farm, for 16 million which is 10 million less than the asking price, the Daily Mail reported online.    
	Bar wish    
	 Los Angeles (PTI): Israeli model Bar Refaeli wants to be the perfect girlfriend to actor Leonardo DiCaprio in order to keep their relationship on the right track. The 25-year-old beauty, who is said to be having an unstable relationship with DiCaprio, wants to prove that she would make a good wife, Showbiz Spy has reported.                                                                                                                                                      
